  "body": "When a user pins a message, system message `user pinned a message` should be visible.\r\n\r\nIt is visible for the other user though.\r\nAnd it's also there after app restart.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1756\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/25482501/595062d5-608a-46ee-ab75-9d9c6b6c48fe\">\r\n\r\n### Reproduce steps\r\n\r\n1. User AAA: Send a message\r\n1. User AAA: Pin a message\r\n1. User B: Note system message `AAA pinned a message`\r\n1. User AAA: Note no system message `AAA pinned a message`\r\n1. User AAA: Restart, note system message `AAAA pinned a message`",
